section
    .container
        h1 Check out
        p Please, press the button below to confirm your order then it will be immedieatly sent to our abstract cosmic human wishes system Lets pretend that we know who your are and where to deliver this order...
        h3 Your order
        ul
            li(ng-repeat="item in vm.cartList")
                | {{ item.name }} &ndash;&nbsp;
                b {{ item.qty }} qty.
        h3
            | Total amount:&nbsp;
            span(ng-bind="vm.totalCount | currency")
        p Actually, all items are free of charge.
        p
            a(href="#" ui-sref="checkOut.confirm").btn.btn-primary.btn-lg Make my wishes come true